WEBVTT

00:00:37.300 --> 00:00:40.580
=Reincarnated Love=

00:00:40.780 --> 00:00:43.700
=Episode 7=

00:00:45.960 --> 00:00:47.960
His Majesty will visit here
in disguise tomorrow.

00:00:48.920 --> 00:00:51.200
Inspect every alley and main road.

00:00:51.710 --> 00:00:53.070
Don't allow the slightest mistake.

00:00:53.330 --> 00:00:54.200
Yes.

00:00:54.320 --> 00:00:55.160
Shitou,

00:00:55.840 --> 00:00:57.430
take your men and secure East Street.

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:01.030
The rest guard the West Market.

00:01:01.750 --> 00:01:02.830
- Move!
- Yes!

00:01:03.150 --> 00:01:03.990
Come with me.

00:01:17.760 --> 00:01:18.870
(On a bitterly cold night,)

00:01:19.840 --> 00:01:20.893
(she's at such an old age.)

00:01:26.840 --> 00:01:27.680
Here.

00:01:33.280 --> 00:01:34.120
Let me.

00:01:37.280 --> 00:01:38.350
Huo Linchuan, be careful!

00:01:43.230 --> 00:01:44.070
Ruoli.

00:01:45.120 --> 00:01:45.960
Troublesome.

00:01:50.560 --> 00:01:52.120
Mr. Huo, are you hurt?

00:01:52.560 --> 00:01:53.400
I'm fine.

00:01:54.120 --> 00:01:54.960
Take her away.

00:01:59.320 --> 00:02:00.586
- Are you okay?
- Are you okay?

00:02:08.080 --> 00:02:08.920
It's so late already.

00:02:09.630 --> 00:02:10.590
Why are you here?

00:02:11.870 --> 00:02:12.800
I just had a dream.

00:02:13.030 --> 00:02:14.310
You were slain by a woman in it.

00:02:14.870 --> 00:02:16.143
I woke up and couldn't find you.

00:02:16.279 --> 00:02:17.589
So, I came out searching for you.

00:02:21.116 --> 00:02:22.749
You risked your life
to save me just now.

00:02:23.190 --> 00:02:24.840
Didn't you fear for your safety?

00:02:26.870 --> 00:02:27.800
The pact has been made.

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:29.560
I'll give my all to honor my promise.

00:02:30.190 --> 00:02:31.590
Would you rather have me do nothing

00:02:31.590 --> 00:02:32.870
when I know you're in danger?

00:02:36.280 --> 00:02:37.280
Was it only for the pact,

00:02:38.960 --> 00:02:39.800
or have you

00:02:41.360 --> 00:02:43.470
come to care for me just a little?

00:02:49.030 --> 00:02:49.870
I...

00:02:55.260 --> 00:02:57.340
ظآزWhere shall I seekظآز

00:02:57.340 --> 00:03:00.300
ظآزThe traces of your past livesظآز

00:03:00.740 --> 00:03:05.820
ظآزI'd spend a lifetime's luck
just for youظآز

00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:10.240
Jiang Ruoli,

00:03:11.030 --> 00:03:12.000
from now on,

00:03:13.870 --> 00:03:15.470
I seek more than just an ally.

00:03:17.770 --> 00:03:22.500
ظآزDreams lift the night
where stars grow thinظآز

00:03:23.290 --> 00:03:28.150
ظآزWhen shall I meet you again
in another lifeظآز

00:03:28.920 --> 00:03:33.520
ظآزThe galaxy stirs;
destiny endlessly returnsظآز

00:03:33.770 --> 00:03:39.190
ظآزIf I could, let me guard you this timeظآز

00:03:39.310 --> 00:03:41.710
ظآزHow did this feeling beginظآز

00:03:42.170 --> 00:03:44.520
ظآزIn each trial, longing deepensظآز

00:03:45.000 --> 00:03:45.840
Jiang Ruoli,

00:03:46.630 --> 00:03:47.510
from now on,

00:03:47.521 --> 00:03:49.379
ظآزWhen the night fades,
the moon shines longerظآز

00:03:49.390 --> 00:03:50.760
I seek more than just an ally.

00:03:50.760 --> 00:03:52.800
ظآزA fleeting dream
shines through the rainظآز

00:03:53.290 --> 00:03:55.740
ظآزThrough three lifetimes,
we never partظآز

00:03:56.000 --> 00:04:01.450
ظآزA thousand years of snow
fall into your palmظآز

00:04:01.590 --> 00:04:04.410
ظآزHow does love fade awayظآز

00:04:04.410 --> 00:04:06.910
ظآزEach thought recalls the pastظآز

00:04:07.210 --> 00:04:09.880
ظآزLonging burns into a lasting acheظآز

00:04:10.150 --> 00:04:12.390
ظآزFrost stains the white robesظآز

00:04:12.850 --> 00:04:15.450
ظآزMist and clouds veil the skyظآز

00:04:15.450 --> 00:04:21.540
(9th lifetime,
Stabbed to death by Ruoli)

00:04:21.870 --> 00:04:22.790
The pact has been made.

00:04:22.920 --> 00:04:24.430
I'll give my all to honor my promise.

00:04:24.990 --> 00:04:26.390
Would you rather have me do nothing

00:04:26.390 --> 00:04:27.530
when I know you're in danger?

00:04:38.420 --> 00:04:39.166
(Stabbed to death)

00:04:43.780 --> 00:04:46.020
(Stabbed to death by Ruoli)

00:05:46.800 --> 00:05:47.640
Milady,

00:05:48.160 --> 00:05:49.000
don't be afraid.

00:05:49.800 --> 00:05:50.640
I am here.

00:05:54.360 --> 00:05:55.200
Last night,

00:05:56.240 --> 00:05:58.040
I took his fatal blow in his stead.

00:05:59.240 --> 00:06:00.360
Yet this piercing heartache

00:06:01.680 --> 00:06:03.190
still haunts my dreams.

00:06:05.270 --> 00:06:06.240
Too great a fright

00:06:06.720 --> 00:06:07.793
often brings on nightmares.

00:06:07.920 --> 00:06:09.480
You'll recover once you calm down.

00:06:18.120 --> 00:06:19.510
Mr. Huo is occupied with duties.

00:06:19.870 --> 00:06:20.950
He left at the Yin hour.

00:06:21.360 --> 00:06:23.150
But before leaving, he told me

00:06:23.430 --> 00:06:25.000
to watch over you by the bed.

00:06:26.270 --> 00:06:27.120
Mind your tongue.

00:06:27.430 --> 00:06:28.360
Who asked you?

00:06:33.390 --> 00:06:34.360
Why haven't I seen Ruyan?

00:06:36.160 --> 00:06:38.190
The storm was wild last night.

00:06:38.190 --> 00:06:39.030
She might've been

00:06:39.240 --> 00:06:40.680
held up with her beloved.

00:06:41.430 --> 00:06:43.750
A young maid like you
shouldn't say such things.

00:06:44.510 --> 00:06:45.950
I was wrong.

00:06:47.680 --> 00:06:48.520
When she returns,

00:06:48.680 --> 00:06:49.630
call her to see me.

00:06:50.750 --> 00:06:52.600
We can't delay her marriage any longer.

00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:53.960
Sure.

00:07:11.800 --> 00:07:12.750
He left at the Yin hour.

00:07:13.270 --> 00:07:14.310
Why is he still not back?

00:07:37.890 --> 00:07:38.750
Jiang Ruoli,

00:07:38.870 --> 00:07:39.710
die!

00:07:47.300 --> 00:07:49.540
(Huo Mansion)

00:07:52.430 --> 00:07:53.270
Are you okay?

00:07:54.040 --> 00:07:54.880
I'm fine.

00:08:00.800 --> 00:08:01.750
Ruyan?

00:08:02.390 --> 00:08:03.230
No.

00:08:04.040 --> 00:08:05.510
She's Ruyan's twin sister,

00:08:05.750 --> 00:08:06.590
Ruyi.

00:08:09.009 --> 00:08:10.702
(The one who tried to kill me
in my dream)

00:08:11.160 --> 00:08:12.040
(was Ruyi.)

00:08:13.160 --> 00:08:14.000
Jiang Ruoli,

00:08:14.390 --> 00:08:15.230
you heartless woman!

00:08:15.390 --> 00:08:16.560
Return my sister's life!

00:08:17.270 --> 00:08:18.360
What did she ever do wrong?

00:08:18.360 --> 00:08:19.600
Why did you drive her to death?

00:08:20.080 --> 00:08:20.950
Miss, calm down.

00:08:20.950 --> 00:08:21.790
What did you say?

00:08:22.830 --> 00:08:23.750
What happened to Ruyan?

00:08:31.720 --> 00:08:32.560
The farewell letter?

00:08:35.440 --> 00:08:36.280
(Ruyi,)

00:08:36.790 --> 00:08:38.790
(by the time you read this,
I'd be dead.)

00:08:39.480 --> 00:08:41.080
(This is of grave consequence.)

00:08:41.639 --> 00:08:43.132
(Ruyan)
(Please don't blame my lady.)

00:08:44.120 --> 00:08:45.550
If I'd arrived a step later today,

00:08:45.750 --> 00:08:47.243
the outcome would've been unthinkable.

00:08:49.840 --> 00:08:51.150
It was all because I was careless

00:08:51.510 --> 00:08:52.960
and failed to notice in time.

00:08:53.440 --> 00:08:54.320
Regarding Ruyan,

00:08:54.320 --> 00:08:55.510
you shouldn't worry too much.

00:08:56.030 --> 00:08:57.630
There may be a misunderstanding.

00:09:00.320 --> 00:09:01.910
Ruyan is like a sister to me.

00:09:02.711 --> 00:09:03.878
After hearing what Ruyi said,

00:09:03.889 --> 00:09:05.099
how could I not be concerned?

00:09:05.750 --> 00:09:08.440
If something truly happened to Ruyan,

00:09:08.550 --> 00:09:09.390
I...

00:09:10.480 --> 00:09:11.539
If you ever need anything,

00:09:11.550 --> 00:09:12.390
just say the word.

00:09:12.600 --> 00:09:14.000
I'll do all I can.

00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:23.550
Earlier, Mr. Lu

00:09:23.550 --> 00:09:25.480
had his arm around Mrs. Huo's waist,

00:09:25.840 --> 00:09:28.270
his jade belt hook brushing
against her gown's folds.

00:09:29.960 --> 00:09:32.000
No wonder Mr. Huo neglects his wife.

00:09:32.270 --> 00:09:35.360
Mr. Lu claimed this place first.

00:09:39.000 --> 00:09:39.873
- Mr. Huo.
- Mr. Huo.

00:09:40.510 --> 00:09:41.350
Get lost.

00:10:26.830 --> 00:10:28.350
ظآزThe dream shatteredظآز

00:10:28.710 --> 00:10:30.390
ظآزLike illusion, yet trueظآز

00:10:30.390 --> 00:10:32.030
ظآزLike a restless soulظآز

00:10:32.910 --> 00:10:34.470
ظآزHow vagueظآز

00:10:34.870 --> 00:10:36.390
ظآزRain and blood, drifting wildظآز

00:10:36.390 --> 00:10:38.630
ظآزA blade of frost in dreamsظآز

00:10:39.430 --> 00:10:42.030
ظآزLove and hate entwinedظآز

00:10:42.510 --> 00:10:45.350
ظآزRise and fall, yet never fadeظآز

00:10:45.990 --> 00:10:50.750
ظآزHow can I turn the tides
of this fleeting lifeظآز

00:10:51.350 --> 00:10:52.870
ظآزWhen fate falls apartظآز

00:10:53.270 --> 00:10:56.830
ظآزMemories return,
carving tears upon my faceظآز

00:10:57.550 --> 00:10:59.110
ظآزYet I can't hold onظآز

00:10:59.510 --> 00:11:03.230
ظآزOnly warmth remains
where longing once burnedظآز

00:11:03.950 --> 00:11:06.790
ظآزLife after lifeظآز

00:11:07.270 --> 00:11:09.950
ظآزFated to meet, but never meant to beظآز

00:11:10.590 --> 00:11:14.670
ظآزStill, I refuse to bow or yieldظآز

00:11:14.750 --> 00:11:17.790
ظآزIn this life, love becomes my bladeظآز

00:11:17.950 --> 00:11:19.350
ظآزTo break free from reincarnationظآز

00:11:19.350 --> 00:11:22.470
ظآزAll past affairs tangled with regretظآز

00:11:22.550 --> 00:11:23.990
ظآزNow shatter apartظآز

00:11:24.110 --> 00:11:27.870
ظآزBy fate and karmic ties confinedظآز

00:11:28.590 --> 00:11:31.390
ظآزIs this fate or calamityظآز

00:11:31.670 --> 00:11:34.510
ظآزIs it life, death, or parting painظآز

00:11:34.830 --> 00:11:39.230
ظآزI ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heartظآز

00:11:39.470 --> 00:11:42.390
ظآزIn the next life, grant me one kissظآز

00:11:42.510 --> 00:11:46.950
ظآزTo kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gazeظآز

00:11:47.150 --> 00:11:52.870
ظآزFor once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never partظآز

00:11:53.310 --> 00:11:56.030
ظآزThis fleeting life feels but a dreamظآز

00:11:56.270 --> 00:11:58.990
ظآزSober or indulgeظآز

00:11:59.430 --> 00:12:05.430
ظآزI only wish to be with you,
with all my heartظآز